<td><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-7624" src="http://www.iwarelogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Fig-11-decision.png" alt="Fig - 11 - decision" width="266" height="95" /></td>
<td><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-7625" src="http://www.iwarelogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Fig-12-decision.png" alt="Fig - 12 - decision" width="284" height="95" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>C. We will set value for OM: Sales Order Form: Cascade Header Changes to Line = Mannual at user level. In this case system will not cascade the header changes to line. The user need to make the changes manually on line.</p>
